         <abstract id="aspace_7ece9ae46361a377aa3aa058a23c93a2">The papers contain correspondence, business, and legal papers documenting the history of the Beaver Creek Ranch Company. Subjects discussed include the managment of the ranch, cattle drivers, and the responsibilities of ranch owners.</abstract>
